videos.headline: VA Tech comes down with wild INT
videos.description: Dez Fitzpatrick bobbles the pass from Malik Cunningham high in the air and it is recovered by Virginia Tech's Divine Deablo.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (VA Tech comes down with wild INT) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: VA Tech takes early lead on Hooker's TD
videos.description: Hendon Hooker takes the handoff and reaches the end zone on a six-yard run to give Virginia Tech an early 7-0 lead over Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (VA Tech takes early lead on Hooker's TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawkins scores monster 90-yard Louisville TD before halftime
videos.description: Javian Hawkins takes the handoff and treks 90 yards untouched down the field to score a Louisville touchdown to cut the Virginia Tech lead to 21-14 before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hawkins scores monster 90-yard Louisville TD before halftime) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fitzpatrick scores 82-yard Louisville TD
videos.description: Malik Cunningham goes deep and completes a pass to Dez Fitzpatrick, who makes his way into the end zone untouched to score an 82-yard Louisville TD.
